<template>
  <select v-model="selectedValue" @change="changeSelect()">
    <option value="서울">서울</option>
    <option value="부산">부산</option>
    <option value="제주">제주</option>
  </select>
</template>



<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      selectedValue: "부산",
    };
  },
  methods: {
    changeSelect(){
      alert(this.selectedValue);
    },
  },
};
</script>


<style scoped>
</style>
